and structurally sound,

04:03.442 --> 04:04.909
just like my mom.

04:04.943 --> 04:06.445
It's ditalini rigati.

04:06.478 --> 04:08.581
Graham, I-I'm gonna be honest with you.

04:08.614 --> 04:11.250
