Angie's 30th birthday.

07:35.748 --> 07:37.990
It's fine. We can just
go to The Karen Club.

07:38.023 --> 07:39.458
No, no, no, no! Don't go!

07:39.490 --> 07:42.461
Look, I promise
we'll keep it civil and quiet.

07:42.494 --> 07:44.497
