08:49.528 --> 08:50.663
Go on.

08:50.696 --> 08:51.764
Look around.

08:51.797 --> 08:53.499
I mean, this is just a-amazing.

08:53.532 --> 08:56.402
I didn't even know
I wanted this party, but <i> he</i> did.

08:56.434 --> 08:58.002
