a-a noble dinosaur.

09:32.471 --> 09:34.273
My favorite is triceratops.

09:34.306 --> 09:35.975
Try to stay with me, Graham.

09:36.008 --> 09:37.942
Dr. Douglas. Welcome back.

09:37.975 --> 09:39.244
