10:30.361 --> 10:31.629
but I hate reading.

10:31.663 --> 10:32.965
You know?

10:32.998 --> 10:35.266
Oof. They don't look happy. Should I...

10:35.299 --> 10:36.709
No. Again, you shouldn't do anything.

10:36.741 --> 10:38.477
What do we know about your instincts?

10:38.503 --> 10:40.139
Leftover water from a hot dog bag.

10:40.172 --> 10:42.141
That's right. You just
keep serving them wine.

10:42.173 --> 10:44.143
